@gailthebrave Have you ever seen a baby sloth ? Probably one of the cutest baby animals you’ll ever see

This one is in a rehabilitation center in the Amazon rainforest. He was recently rescued from wildlife trafficking, which is why he’s currently being placed in a box.💙🦥

Unfortunately they often kill the mother to use the baby as pets or for tourism purposes. 

Rehabilitating baby sloths involves providing specialized care, mimicking their natural environment, and addressing health issues. This includes proper nutrition, social interaction, and a gradual reintroduction to the wild when they are ready. It’s crucial to collaborate with experts and follow ethical practices to ensure their successful rehabilitation.
